videos.headline: South Alabama strikes 1st with 45-yard TD pass
videos.description: Following a fumble recovery by the South Alabama defense, Cole Garvin lofts a pass over the middle to Jamarius Way for a 45-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: South Alabama's Way catches 2nd TD pass
videos.description: Jamarius Way burns the Coastal Carolina defense and Evan Orth finds him wide open over the middle for a 73-yard South Alabama touchdown.

videos.headline: Coastal Carolina scores on 31-yard pass
videos.description: Bryce Carpenter connects with Isaiah Likely for a 31-yard touchdown to put Coastal Carolina on the board in the 2nd quarter.

videos.headline: Coastal Carolina's Makins ejected for throwing punch
videos.description: Coastal Carolina linebacker Michael Makins throws a punch at South Alabama's Jamarius Way and gets ejected late in the 4th quarter.
